* Add Notebook\nTask to Job
** What It Is
***_ Runs a notebook as a job step
***_ Specify notebook path
***_ Configure compute & parameters
** DAG Representation
***_ Each task = node in DAG
***_ Visual execution flow
***_ Shows dependencies visually
** Typical Pipeline
***_ Ingestion notebook
***_ Transformation notebook
***_ Load to final table notebook
** Key Point
***_ Without dependencies = chaos
***_ Dependencies = correct order
@endmindmap
